title: At-home care
itunes:title: At-home care
description: In this episode, we explore the latest thinking and newest innovations in at-home care for seniors. Guests include AgeWave founders,Doctors Ken and Maddy Dychtwald, our own Adam Pellegrini (SVP Enterprise Virtual Care & Consumer Health), and health care futurist Zayna Khayat (author of The Future of Aging).
